---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getGameConfig } from '@/lib/data';
const config = getGameConfig();
---
<BaseLayout title={`Privacy Policy - ${config.game.name} Guide`} description={`Privacy policy for the unofficial ${config.game.name} fan site. Learn how we handle analytics, cookies, and third-party services.`} canonical="/privacy-policy/">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 31, 2026</p>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">1. Overview</p>
        <p>This website ("Site") is an unofficial fan-made companion site for the Roblox game "{config.game.name}". We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we handle information when you visit our Site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">2. Information We Collect</p>
        <p><strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Personal Data:</strong> We do not collect, store, or process any personal data. We do not require account registration, login, or any form of user identification.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Usage Data:</strong> We collect anonymous usage data through third-party analytics services (see Section 3). This includes page views, referral sources, device type, browser, and general geographic region. This data cannot be used to identify any individual person.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">3. Google Analytics (GA4)</p>
        <p>We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use our Site. GA4 collects information such as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
          <li>Traffic source (how you found our Site)</li>
          <li>Device type, browser, and operating system</li>
          <li>Approximate geographic location (country/city level)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">GA4 data is anonymized and aggregated. We do not link analytics data to any individual. For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">4. Advertising Networks</p>
        <p>We use third-party advertising networks to display ads on our Site. These ad networks may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to serve relevant advertisements. Ad networks we use include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Adsterra / EffectiveCPMNetwork</li>
          <li>HighPerformanceFormat (Monetag)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">These services may collect information about your browsing behavior across different websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising through:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li><a href="https://optout.networkadvertising.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Network Advertising Initiative Opt-Out</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">European Interactive Digital Advertising Alliance</a></li>
          <li>Your browser's Do Not Track settings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">5. Cookies</p>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device. Our Site uses cookies for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — Set by Google Analytics (_ga, _ga_*). Used to distinguish users and measure site usage. These cookies last up to 2 years.</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong> — Set by our ad partners. Used to deliver relevant ads and measure ad performance.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect site functionality.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">6. Local Storage</p>
        <p>Our calculators may use your browser's local storage to save your input values between sessions (e.g., muscle amount, selected pet). This data never leaves your device and is not transmitted to any server.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">7. Third-Party Links</p>
        <p>Our Site may contain links to external websites, including Roblox, YouTube, and other third-party services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">8. Children's Privacy</p>
        <p>Our Site is designed as a general-audience resource for a Roblox game. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age. If you believe a child has provided personal data to any of our third-party services, please contact us so we can take appropriate action.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">9. Data Security</p>
        <p>Since we do not collect or store personal data on our servers, there is minimal risk of data breach. Our Site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages, which provides SSL encryption and industry-standard security measures.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">10. Changes to This Policy</p>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">11. Contact</p>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
